snippet.title: Best VGM 2081 - Miitopia - Battle ­~ The Sky Scraper
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2187 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wv6HHTa4jjI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Miitopia (2016)
Battle ­~ The Sky Scraper (World 6)
Toshiyuki Sudo, Shinji Ushiroda, Yumi Takahashi & Megumi Inoue
